      • setUnderlineThickness

        public void setUnderlineThickness(int underlineThickness)
        Sets the new underline thickness. If the specified thickness is negative, then the thickness is set to 1. If the specified thickness is greater than the font height, then the thickness is set to the font height. If the font height is greater than Byte.MAX_VALUE, then the thickness is set to Byte.MAX_VALUE.
        Parameters:
        underlineThickness - The new underline thickness.
